{"tid":821664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無欋十號風球! 國際性比賽Magic Grand Prix Hong Kong如期在九展舉行!","createTime":"2018-09-16T04:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T04:27:29.000Z","uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c1aa6ed7a10e6f96ef552ae19d0b028608c4ae57","tid":821664,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:27:29.000Z","msg":"無欋十號風球! Magic Grand Prix Hong Kong如期在九展舉行!<br />\n連帶另一個區域性重要比賽PTQ, 亦風雨不改舉行!<br />\n<a href=\"https://magic.wizards.com/en/events/coverage/gphk18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmagic.wizards.com%2Fen%2Fevents%2Fcoverage%2Fgphk18&d=J87RtKDw3DQ2Dt8jYY%2BwFDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3c3e18b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://magic.wizards.com/en/events/coverage/gphk18</a><br />\n<br />\n嗯, 琴日有幸晉級D選手慘囉, 要冒風雨坐的士去會場~<br />\n不過, 有D日本職業選手, 領教過之前打日本果個風, 一早已取消行程, 罕有缺席區內的重要比賽!<br />\n<br />\nPS 琴日我都去左, 不過無參加main event, 只係好hea咁周圍行, 打左鋪外圍小比賽....琴日4點幾, 聽到主辦單位話如期舉行, 真係比個勇字佢地...........<br />\n<br />\nfrom twitter: 十號風球下, 九展比賽場地外的情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/magicprotour/status/1041160262378676224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmagicprotour%2Fstatus%2F1041160262378676224&d=J87RtKDw3DQ2Dt8jYY%2BwFDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2cc487fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmagicprotour%2Fstatus%2F1041160262378676224&h=a156e106\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/magicprotour/status/1041160262378676224</a>"}]}